---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Information" />
<section
	class="w-[80%] h-full m-auto flex flex-col items-start my-40"
	id="information">
	<article class="border-l-4 pl-4 max-w-[75ch]">
		<span class="opacity-60 text-1xl flex items-center gap-1"></span>
		The all in one Esg Platform
		<h5 class="text-2xl font-bold text-pretty flex flex-col opacity-80">
			Intresting Information
			<strong>About these points</strong>
			Future proof your company with Cacta, contact us...
		</h5>
	</article>

	<article class="parent my-10">
		<div class="div1">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Environment</span
			>
			<h2>Emissions</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>~ Global Warming Potential (incl. Scope 1, 2, 3)</p>
			<p>~ Air Quality (incl. PM, SO3,NO2, volatile organic compounds)</p>
			<p>
				~ Eutrophication Potential (incl. Fresh, marine, and terrestial
				Waters)
			</p>
			<p>~ Ozone Depletion Potential</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div2">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Environment</span
			>
			<h2>Resources</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>
				~ Electricity use (incl. consumption, GHG emisions, share of
				renewables, intensity)
			</p>
			<p>~ Energy use (incl. consumption, GHG emissions, intensity)</p>
			<p>~ Water Use (incl. Water withdrawal, discharge, consume)</p>
			<p>~ Land use (incl. disturbed, reclaimed, footprint)</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div3">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Environment</span
			>
			<h2>Waste</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>~ Mineral Waste (incl. total, waste intensity)</p>
			<p>~ Non-Mineral Waste (incl. total, waste intensity)</p>
			<p>~ Hazardous vs Non-hazardous</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div4">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Social</span
			>
			<h2>Health and Safety</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>
				~ Total recordable injuries (incl. Lost time frequency, lost
				time disabling injuries frequency, fatality rate)
			</p>
			<p>
				~ Total potential incidents (incl. Frequency, high potential
				incident, serious HPI, process related HPI)
			</p>
			<p>
				~ Occupational diseases (incl. Respiratory disorders, hearing
				loss, musculoskeletal disorders)
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div5">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Social</span
			>
			<h2>People and Culture</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>
				~ Workforce (incl. Male, female, non-binary, age and level
				distribution)
			</p>
			<p>
				~ Retention (incl. Turnover, parental leave, return rate of
				parental leave, retention after 12 months)
			</p>
			<p>
				~ Development (incl. Training investments, hours of training for
				staff/non-staff)
			</p>
			<p>
				~ Remuneration (incl. Entry level vs. median local wage, highest
				vs. median wage, salary increase)
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div6">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Social</span
			>
			<h2>Relation with communities</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>~ Grievancies and disputes</p>
			<p>~ Total economic value generated and distributed</p>
			<p>~ Local employment and expenditure</p>
			<p>~ Expenditures on self declared indigenous suppliers</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div7">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Governance</span
			>
			<h2>Corporate Governance</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>~ Claims for corruption and bribery</p>
			<p>
				~ Number of initiatives related to corporate/governance risk
				management
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="div8">
			<span class="w-full flex opacity-20 justify-end font-semibold"
				>Governance</span
			>
			<h2>Supply Chain Management</h2>
			<hr />
			<p>~ Total expenditures on suppliers</p>
			<p>~ Percentage of total expenditures in local suppliers</p>
			<p>~ Percentage of indigeneous suppliers</p>
		</div>
	</article>
</section>

<style>
	h2 {
		display: grid;
		color: var(--text-1);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	p {
		line-height: 1rem;
		text-wrap: pretty;
		color: var(--text-2);
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	.parent {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
		grid-template-rows: repeat(6, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
		width: 100%;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.parent > div {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: start;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-items: center;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		background: hsl(0 0% 0% / 0.09);
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text-1);
	}
	.parent > div:hover {
		cursor: crosshair;
		transform: scale(1.1);
		filter: brightness(1.2);
	}

	.div1 {
		grid-area: 1 / 1 / 3 / 3;
	}
	.div2 {
		grid-area: 1 / 3 / 3 / 5;
	}
	.div3 {
		grid-area: 1 / 5 / 3 / 7;
	}
	.div4 {
		grid-area: 3 / 1 / 5 / 3;
	}
	.div5 {
		grid-area: 3 / 3 / 5 / 5;
	}
	.div6 {
		grid-area: 3 / 5 / 5 / 7;
	}
	.div7 {
		grid-area: 5 / 1 / 7 / 4;
	}
	.div8 {
		grid-area: 5 / 4 / 7 / 7;
	}
	@media (width < 1200px) {
		section {
			width: 96%;
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}
		.parent {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
			gap: 1rem;
		}
		.parent > div {
			grid-area: auto;
		}
		.parent > div:hover {
			cursor: crosshair;
			transform: none;
			filter: brightness(1.2);
		}
	}
	hr {
		height: 2px;
		width: 10ch;
		border: none;
		background: LinkText;
		background: linear-gradient(
				to bottom right in oklab,
				oklch(70% 0.5 340),
				oklch(90% 0.5 200)
			)
			fixed;
	}

	article {
		border-color: #63e;
		height: auto;
	}
	strong {
		font-size: 3rem;
		background: radial-gradient(125% 125% at 50% 10%, #000 00%, #63e 50%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		color: transparent;
		line-height: 4rem;
	}
</style>
